{"id": "1243408589813579816", "channel_id": "1242675875296837652", "type": 0, "author_id": "703641666489286727", "author_name": "fengliyaowo", "author_bot": false, "content": "仔細想想好像可以試著寫看看<:stoppage:1236938521365839872> \n被do到失去理智的守密人還有腹黑鯊鯊", "timestamp": "2024-05-24T03:41:49.226000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1242675875296837652", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "與鯊魚瘋狂炒飯那檔事-完結(?)  等待開第二坑", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969"}
